": "van_t1000e", "user_id": "1317710769881616537", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1317710769881616537/0adbbf68da9a10ac526cca94c4b72cb7.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Thursday, February 26, 2026 9:48 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-02-26 9:48 p.m.", "text": "https://heltec.org/project/wifi-lora-32-v4-expansion-housing/ https://zbm2industries.com/products/mesh-ceramic-filter https://illumn.com/18650-vapcell-n41-4050mah-12-5a-high-capacity-flat-top-li-ion-battery.html https://a.co/d/0ae4LUo7 @David (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><a href=\"https://heltec.org/project/wifi-lora-32-v4-expansion-housing/\">https://heltec.org/project/wifi-lora-32-v4-expansion-housing/</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://zbm2industries.com/products/mesh-ceramic-filter\">https://zbm2industries.com/products/mesh-ceramic-filter</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://illumn.com/18650-vapcell-n41-4050mah-12-5a-high-capacity-flat-top-li-ion-battery.html\">https://illumn.com/18650-vapcell-n41-4050mah-12-5a-high-capacity-flat-top-li-ion-battery.html</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://a.co/d/0ae4LUo7\">https://a.co/d/0ae4LUo7</a>\n\n<span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\" title=\"david2342\">@David</span></span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Thursday, February 26, 2026 9:51 p.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": ["<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=\"chatlog__embed-color-pill chatlog__embed-color-pill--default\"></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-author-container><a class=chatlog__embed-author-link href=\"https://heltec.org/author/richard3366/\"><div class=chatlog__embed-author>richard3366</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=\"https://heltec.org/project/wifi-lora-32-v4-expansion-housing/\"><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">WiFi LoRa 32 Expansion Kit</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-description><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">The WiFi LoRa 32 V4 Expansion Kit already includes V4 and pre-installed accessories. You can also customize your own hardware via the MQB platform.\n\n \tNote:&#160;Selecting the battery option will significantly increase shipping costs.</div></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/xVa4WJUPbvgWXDVL1dHR3MNQQcUkOnIvsyolwDTEt3k/https/heltec.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/v422.png> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/xVa4WJUPbvgWXDVL1dHR3MNQQcUkOnIvsyolwDTEt3k/https/heltec.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/v422.png alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=https://heltec.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/v422.png> </a></div></div></div></div>", "<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=\"chatlog__embed-color-pill chatlog__embed-color-pill--default\"></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=https://zbm2industries.com/products/mesh-ceramic-filter><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">Mesh Ceramic Filter</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-description><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">A ceramic filter for the ISM band. These bandpass filters are some of the absolute best I’ve used in my builds. This filters out RFI from Cell towers and UHF TV Sites. They are tuned for 915 +/- 13MHz. Simply put them in line of the antenna and watch your range for both transmit and reception improve!&#160;Spec:Passband: 91</div></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/B-7OhgmlxJKAT5OnczNschBgrgEVtqR2cn6zuHSz9I8/%3Fv%3D1766772557/http/zbm2industries.com/cdn/shop/files/IMG-2127.heic> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/B-7OhgmlxJKAT5OnczNschBgrgEVtqR2cn6zuHSz9I8/%3Fv%3D1766772557/http/zbm2industries.com/cdn/shop/files/IMG-2127.heic alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=\"http://zbm2industries.com/cdn/shop/files/IMG-2127.heic?v=1766772557\"> </a></div></div></div></div>", "<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=\"chatlog__embed-color-pill chatlog__embed-color-pill--default\"></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=https://illumn.com/18650-vapcell-n41-4050mah-12-5a-high-capacity-flat-top-li-ion-battery.html><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">18650 Vapcell N41 4050mAh 12.5A High Capacity Flat Top Li-ion Battery</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-description><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">18650 Vapcell N41 4050mAh 12.5A High Capacity Flat Top Li-ion Battery</div></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/Cl__Qd-sN36gbeAmETRWNc4UmMVTb2460_NbKjbJUnI/https/illumn.com/media/catalog/product/cache/8ad104451f814e6905b334b3a42711d7/v/a/vapcelln41flattop.jpg> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/Cl__Qd-sN36gbeAmETRWNc4UmMVTb2460_NbKjbJUnI/https/illumn.com/media/catalog/product/cache/8ad104451f814e6905b334b3a42711d7/v/a/vapcelln41flattop.jpg alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=https://illumn.com/media/catalog/product/cache/8ad104451f814e6905b334b3a42711d7/v/a/vapcelln41flattop.jpg> </a></div></div></div></div>", "<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=\"chatlog__embed-color-pill chatlog__embed-color-pill--default\"></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=https://a.co/d/0ae4LUo7><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">Muzi 915Mhz Whip Antenna - Upgrade Your LoRa and Meshtastic Perform...</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-description><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">Upgrade your antenna to this flexible whip design. Improves performance, measured SWR of 1.3 compared with the stock stubby antenna at a SWR of 3.5. SWR is a measure of transmission efficiency, how much power from the LoRa radio makes it out into the world via the antenna. SWR 1.3 = 98% efficient...</div></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/f35EQx411rR9jS3_2A0Vqxh9_QzrPRpyuYPa6h1am2M/https/m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41DjbRkOjUL.jpg_BO30%2C255%2C255%2C255_UF750%2C750_SR1910%2C1000%2C0%2CC_QL100_.jpg> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/f35EQx411rR9jS3_2A0Vqxh9_QzrPRpyuYPa6h1am2M/https/m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41DjbRkOjUL.jpg_BO30%2C255%2C255%2C255_UF750%2C750_SR1910%2C1000%2C0%2CC_QL100_.jpg alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41DjbRkOjUL.jpg_BO30,255,255,255_UF750,750_SR1910,1000,0,C_QL100_.jpg> </a></div></div></div></div>"], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1480297102977532250", "author": "David", "author_handle": "david2342", "user_id": "718454652324151316", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Sunday, March 8, 2026 4:12 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-03-08 4:12 p.m.", "text": "Thanks! I am still hoping to find a standalone device compatible with FOSS meshcore firmware, but I think that doesn't exist yet. The rest sounds great.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdo